trans-unit.source: This attribute supports <xref uid="langword_csharp_My.Forms" name="My.Forms" href=""></xref> and <xref uid="langword_csharp_My.WebServices" name="My.WebServices" href=""></xref> in [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)].
This attribute supports `My.Forms` and `My.WebServices` in [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)].
It is not intended to be used directly from your code.

When this attribute is put on a class, the compiler fills that class with properties corresponding to all the types in the project that derive from the type specified by the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.MyGroupCollectionAttribute.MyGroupName%2A> property.
